159
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,970
Phuak: The first choice.

160
00:06:04,970 --> 00:06:07,170
Ink: How about this? For the first pair,

161
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,950
-Ink: I'll let you choose.
-Phuak: Just take both of us.

162
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,630
Jeff: You're letting me pick first?

163
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:11,780
Ink: Yeah, because everyone
wants to be on your team.

164
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:13,250
[Ink is starting to get angry!]

165
00:06:11,970 --> 00:06:13,300
Oat: Hey, that's not it.

166
00:06:13,330 --> 00:06:15,250
[So that's how it is]

167
00:06:13,330 --> 00:06:14,530
Phuak: Just wait.

168
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:17,150
Jeff: Okay, I've decided.

169
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:19,330
Phuak: If I were him, I'd pick you too.

170
