[Expectation...]

171
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:26,660
Jeff: Phuak…

172
00:06:26,810 --> 00:06:28,780
-Jeff: Phuak...
-Phuak: Hey!

173
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:29,510
