174
00:06:30,370 --> 00:06:31,630
Jeff: go to Ink's team!

175
00:06:33,490 --> 00:06:34,460
Jeff: Go to Ink's team!

176
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:35,500
[Happy times are always short-lived]

177
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:39,000
[Jeff chose Oat]

178
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:42,380
[Ink is very satisfied with this]

179
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:46,570
[Life really isn't easy]

180
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:49,550
