-Phuak: It's okay, it's okay.

181
00:06:49,850 --> 00:06:52,420
[Teams set! Line up!]

182
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:56,870
Oat: Okay, let's go.

183
00:06:56,970 --> 00:06:59,750
[Setting off to find the next team member, GO!]

184
00:06:57,570 --> 00:07:00,070
Phuak: They've already
entered the zone, Captain.

185
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:02,910
