-Phuak: I don't know, Captain, don't step on my foot.

186
00:07:02,910 --> 00:07:05,390
[Who will be the next person waiting?]

187
00:07:05,490 --> 00:07:07,570
[Jeff's team strolls in, all relaxed]

188
