Phuak: When will we arrive?

191
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,920
Ink: Can I switch teammates?

192
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:14,090
[Who will be the next waiting member?]

193
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,540
Oat: 1, 2, 1, 2, 1, 2.

194
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:16,170
Phuak: When will we arrive?

195
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:19,550
[Group 2: NuNew & Tay]

196
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:16,730
Tay: What?

197
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:19,390
Tay: This feels like a drama.

198
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:22,230
Tay: I want to go to Ink's team.

199
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:24,490
-Ink: Tay.
-Tay: I want to go to Ink's team.

200
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:26,480
[Only has eyes for Jeff]

201
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,480
Tay: I want to go to Ink's team.

202
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:30,630
[A total mess]

203
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:34,159
Tay: Jeff, Jeff!

204
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:35,250
[Things are getting messy]

205
00:07:35,490 --> 00:07:37,230
-Oat: Separate first.
-Phuak: Separate, separate.

206
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:39,050
[Step back first
and sort out the situation!]

207
00:07:37,530 --> 00:07:39,210
Oat: Let him decide.

208
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,340
Ink: I'm giving Tay a chance.

209
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:42,260
[Ink is giving Tay a chance]

210
00:07:41,470 --> 00:07:43,170
Ink: Because in my heart, Tay no longer

211
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:45,100
Ink: has any "good guy" image left.

212
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,110
Ink: He completely ruined his image.

213
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:48,170
Ink: Because he ripped
off my name tag

214
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,270
Ink: and lied to me.

215
00:07:51,230 --> 00:07:55,550
[Since the first episode, Tay
was the one who ripped off Ink's name tag]

216
00:07:55,890 --> 00:07:57,280
Tay: I'm sorry.

217
00:07:56,690 --> 00:08:02,850
[And Phuak also came over to help]

218
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,990
Ink: Tay.

219
00:08:05,990 --> 00:08:08,990
Ink: Why did you grab my hair?

220
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:11,530
[He's basically on trial in Ink's eyes]

221
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:15,080
[So this is a chance to redeem himself]

222
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,340
Jeff: I want him on our team, too.

223
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:20,630
NuNew: I don't want
to stay in this team, either.

224
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:24,000
Phuak: Look at me, look at me, Tay.

225
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:26,090
[Why is fate so cruel?]

226
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:26,670
Phuak: Tay, Tay.

227
00:08:26,730 --> 00:08:27,910
Phuak: Welcome!

228
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:28,910
[NuNew joined Jeff's team]

229
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:30,150
Tay: I wanted to be
on your team all along.

230
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:32,030
[Of course, I want to stay with Ink]

231
00:08:30,370 --> 00:08:31,890
Tay: I've got everything covered.

232
00:08:31,890 --> 00:08:34,130
Tay: Leave everything to me.

233
00:08:34,669 --> 00:08:37,190
Ink: Fine, your wish is granted. Come here.

234
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:38,350
