235
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:38,340
Tay: I'm so happy.

236
00:08:38,610 --> 00:08:41,169
[May the gods bless me]

237
00:08:39,710 --> 00:08:42,039
-Ink: What's wrong?
-Phuak: Come closer.

238
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,400
Ink: Is Tay about to cry?

239
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:47,130
Tay: Our team is basically
the "justice squad."

240
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:50,410
-Jeff: Already starting to go crazy?
-Tay: I've already lost it. I'm going to destroy everything.

241
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:51,120
[About to go all out!]

242
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:59,120
[Heading to the next location!]

243
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:56,120
Tay: 1, 2, 3.

244
00:08:56,200 --> 00:09:00,850
Tay: 1, 2, 3, middle, middle-left,
middle-right.

245
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:13,480
1, 2, 3, 4. 1, 2, 1, 2, 1, 2.

