2273
01:15:15,090 --> 01:15:15,190
[Phuak is being targeted]

2274
01:15:15,700 --> 01:15:18,630
-NuNew: We'll surround them.
-Oat: Close in on them.

2275
01:15:19,380 --> 01:15:21,040
Daou: Offroad is coming down.

2276
01:15:21,240 --> 01:15:22,900
Daou: Phuak, get out of there.

2277
01:15:23,420 --> 01:15:24,480
Phuak: Okay, okay.

2278
01:15:25,290 --> 01:15:28,090
[Hearing it on the walkie,
he hides immediately]

2279
01:15:28,100 --> 01:15:29,260
Oat: Let's go.

2280
01:15:30,210 --> 01:15:32,850
[Passing Daou, they head straight for Phuak]

2281
01:15:31,100 --> 01:15:32,700
Oat: Go down, straight down.

2282
01:15:33,440 --> 01:15:34,800
Daou: Go, Phuak!

2283
01:15:36,040 --> 01:15:36,970
Daou: Go, Phuak!

2284
01:15:42,530 --> 01:15:44,890
[They spot a Rabbit]

2285
01:15:42,890 --> 01:15:44,900
Offroad: Rabbit, the Rabbit is here.

2286
01:15:44,900 --> 01:15:46,120
Oat: Let's do it, just do it.

2287
01:15:45,410 --> 01:15:48,090
[Ignore Phuak
and take on the Rabbit's challenge]

2288
01:15:46,560 --> 01:15:48,100
Oat: We're doing the game.

2289
01:15:48,490 --> 01:15:50,970
[What's the mission here?]

2290
01:15:51,530 --> 01:15:53,770
[Mission: Defuse the time bomb]

2291
01:15:54,210 --> 01:15:56,490
[The bomb is connected to 5 wires]

2292
01:15:57,050 --> 01:15:59,450
[Cut the wrong one and it explodes instantly.
Only one wire is safe]

2293
01:16:00,210 --> 01:16:04,090
[Cut wrong or exceed 1 minute
= mission failed]

2294
01:16:04,610 --> 01:16:07,490
[Oat prepares to start]

2295
01:16:08,450 --> 01:16:11,010
[The countdown begins]

2296
01:16:11,770 --> 01:16:14,130
[Nervous]

2297
01:16:14,610 --> 01:16:16,810
[Only a 1-in-5 chance]

2298
01:16:17,840 --> 01:16:18,970
Oat: I'm cutting it.

2299
01:16:20,290 --> 01:16:22,370
[Wrong cut = explosion]

2300
01:16:20,820 --> 01:16:23,560
Oat: I'll pick black.

2301
01:16:26,330 --> 01:16:28,890
[Chooses by instinct]

2302
01:16:30,570 --> 01:16:31,810
[Cuts without hesitation]

2303
01:16:32,570 --> 01:16:35,010
[Is it going to explode?]

2304
01:16:40,850 --> 01:16:43,370
[The countdown stops]

2305
01:16:44,690 --> 01:16:48,010
[Mission cleared on the first try!]

2306
01:16:47,010 --> 01:16:49,240
Oat: I won, I won.
I got extra time, right?

2307
01:16:49,240 --> 01:16:49,940
Rabbit: Yes.

2308
01:16:49,650 --> 01:16:52,810
[Green Team gains 10 extra minutes]

2309
01:16:53,130 --> 01:16:55,410
[Meanwhile, Offroad is chasing Phuak]

2310
01:16:53,220 --> 01:16:54,550
Offroad: NuNew, NuNew!

2311
01:16:58,080 --> 01:17:01,340
Phuak: Hey, they're done over there. It's done.

2312
01:17:03,170 --> 01:17:05,290
[NuNew chases from behind]

2313
01:17:06,210 --> 01:17:10,330
[Shakes off the pursuit and escapes]

2314
01:17:10,930 --> 01:17:13,130
[Jeff comes out immediately]

2315
01:17:11,100 --> 01:17:12,360
Oat: Jeff's out.

2316
01:17:13,810 --> 01:17:16,490
[Jeff is coming]

2317
01:17:17,300 --> 01:17:19,640
Jeff: Go after him. Lure Daou over.

2318
01:17:19,890 --> 01:17:21,970
[They spot Daou alone]

2319
01:17:20,340 --> 01:17:22,270
Jeff: Daou is running to the right.

2320
01:17:22,360 --> 01:17:24,640
-Offroad: He's running.
-Oat: It's fine. Run over and cut him off.

2321
01:17:22,410 --> 01:17:25,530
[Charge in and grab him!]

2322
01:17:25,690 --> 01:17:27,330
[They shift their focus to Daou]

2323
01:17:29,380 --> 01:17:30,540
Daou: I'm being surrounded.

2324
01:17:30,540 --> 01:17:33,200
Daou: I'm being surrounded
by Jeff and Offroad.

2325
01:17:34,100 --> 01:17:35,830
Ink: Daou is being surrounded.

2326
01:17:37,180 --> 01:17:38,840
Ink: Should we go support him?

2327
01:17:39,080 --> 01:17:40,260
Daou: No, no.

2328
01:17:40,260 --> 01:17:42,260
Daou: I'll send you a signal in a bit.

2329
01:17:42,810 --> 01:17:47,090
[Buys time by luring Green Team along]

2330
01:17:55,500 --> 01:17:56,760
Daou: I'm surrounded.

2331
01:17:57,730 --> 01:18:00,290
[Jeff appears in front]

2332
01:17:58,420 --> 01:18:00,080
Daou: My throat hurts so much.

2333
01:18:00,120 --> 01:18:03,780
Jeff: I found Daou. Come over.

2334
01:18:00,450 --> 01:18:03,090
[I found Daou. Come quick]
[I'm surrounded]

2335
01:18:04,180 --> 01:18:07,820
Jeff: H-He ran back the same way.
He's heading back where he came from.

2336
01:18:04,490 --> 01:18:07,890
[Runs immediately]

2337
01:18:09,970 --> 01:18:12,690
[Blocked by Oat]

2338
01:18:12,690 --> 01:18:15,730
-Oat: It's fine, come on.
-Daou: Guys, I'm about to get my name tag ripped.

2339
01:18:15,730 --> 01:18:17,970
[Calls for urgent support]

2340
01:18:15,730 --> 01:18:16,660
Daou: No!

2341
01:18:17,980 --> 01:18:20,540
-Ink: Are we going? All four, let's go.
-Mike: Yeah, go help him.

2342
01:18:18,290 --> 01:18:20,330
[Let's go!]

2343
01:18:20,370 --> 01:18:23,370
[Pink Team mobilizes quickly]

2344
01:18:24,050 --> 01:18:27,090
[Daou buys time,
waiting for teammates to save him]

2345
01:18:27,100 --> 01:18:28,360
Jeff: Hey, be careful.

2346
01:18:31,850 --> 01:18:34,450
[Corner him and finish him]

2347
01:18:35,050 --> 01:18:36,250
[Rip!]

2348
01:18:36,810 --> 01:18:38,170
[Rip!]

2349
01:18:38,170 --> 01:18:39,320
Oat: It's done.

2350
01:18:38,330 --> 01:18:41,130
[His name tag is finally ripped]

2351
01:18:41,130 --> 01:18:45,680
PD: Daou is out.

2352
01:18:41,570 --> 01:18:45,290
[Daou is out]

2353
01:18:45,290 --> 01:18:48,490
[Name-Tag Ripping result;
Green Team vs Pink Team]

2354
01:18:49,380 --> 01:18:51,160
PD: Daou is out.

2355
01:18:51,160 --> 01:18:53,160
PD: Daou is out.

2356
01:18:53,920 --> 01:18:55,920
-PD: Daou is out.
-Ink: Come back, everyone, come back.

2357
01:18:54,290 --> 01:18:57,770
[On the way to support,
they hear a teammate is out]

2358
01:19:00,850 --> 01:19:05,130
[Let's go chase Pink Team]

2359
01:19:01,220 --> 01:19:01,980
Offroad: It's Phuak.

2360
01:19:01,980 --> 01:19:05,780
-Offroad: Only Phuak is alone.
-NuNew: Oat, they're all over there.

2361
01:19:06,980 --> 01:19:09,480
Ink: Come back, everyone, come back.

2362
01:19:08,930 --> 01:19:13,010
[Pink Team scatters in different directions]

2363
01:19:13,540 --> 01:19:16,220
Ink: Come back, everyone, come back.

2364
01:19:17,930 --> 01:19:19,690
[No response from teammates]

2365
01:19:20,410 --> 01:19:22,290
[This puts everyone in danger]

2366
01:19:22,370 --> 01:19:25,610
[Request recall!]

2367
01:19:22,370 --> 01:19:23,500
Ink: Requesting a team recall.

2368
01:19:25,620 --> 01:19:31,740
PD: Pink Team requests to use their recall.

2369
01:19:25,970 --> 01:19:34,970
[Pink Team requests to recall members!]

2370
01:19:31,740 --> 01:19:34,780
PD: Everyone return to the Time-Free Room.

2371
01:19:34,970 --> 01:19:37,770
[ During the game,
the captain can call the team back once]

2372
01:19:37,770 --> 01:19:40,570
[When activated, the game pauses and all members
return to the Time-Free Room]

2373
01:19:41,050 --> 01:19:44,210
[Pink Team has 28 minutes remaining]

2374
01:19:44,220 --> 01:19:46,350
Ink: I think we go with a 4-person plan.

2375
01:19:46,460 --> 01:19:48,680
Tay: Everyone goes out, then split up
to reduce risk.

2376
01:19:48,680 --> 01:19:50,940
Mike: Our plan now
is to go all in.

2377
01:19:50,940 --> 01:19:53,100
-Mike: There's no other way.
-Phuak: Right.

2378
01:19:53,100 --> 01:19:55,210
-Tay: We have to go for it.
-Ink: We fight them head-on.

2379
01:19:55,210 --> 01:19:58,090
[Time to go all in]

2380
01:19:55,360 --> 01:19:58,400
-Phuak: One big push, all or nothing.
-Ink: Let's give it a shot.

2381
01:19:58,400 --> 01:20:00,680
Phuak: Maybe we get lucky
and run into a Rabbit.

2382
01:19:59,610 --> 01:20:02,890
[All members will head out.
With luck, they might find a Rabbit]

2383
01:20:01,140 --> 01:20:02,890
Phuak: But thinning their numbers first
might be better.

2384
01:20:02,890 --> 01:20:04,040
Oat: Alright. Wow.

2385
01:20:03,330 --> 01:20:05,730
[Green Team has 52 minutes remaining]

2386
01:20:04,040 --> 01:20:05,300
Jeff: You're amazing.

2387
01:20:06,050 --> 01:20:08,890
[Green Team doesn't need to rush]

2388
01:20:06,050 --> 01:20:08,720
Jeff: Now we just focus on time.

2389
01:20:09,280 --> 01:20:10,880
Oat: The game is almost over.

2390
01:20:11,140 --> 01:20:12,660
Jeff: From here on, we can take it easy.

2391
01:20:11,170 --> 01:20:12,650
[Easy breezy]

2392
01:20:12,660 --> 01:20:17,520
PD: Recall time is over.
Return to the Name-Tag Ripping Game.

2393
01:20:13,490 --> 01:20:19,730
[Recall time ends.
The game resumes]

2394
01:20:17,520 --> 01:20:19,730
PD: Recall time is over.

2395
01:20:20,240 --> 01:20:21,600
-Phuak: Let's go.
-Ink: Let's go.

2396
01:20:21,210 --> 01:20:24,250
[Move out as planned]

2397
01:20:22,280 --> 01:20:24,690
-Phuak: All four together.
-Ink: Take the elevator.

2398
01:20:24,690 --> 01:20:26,690
[More members means time drains faster]

2399
01:20:27,490 --> 01:20:32,570
[Green Team sends out Offroad and Engfa]

2400
01:20:28,080 --> 01:20:29,680
Offroad: They're coming up.

2401
01:20:34,120 --> 01:20:36,320
Offroad: They're taking the elevator.

2402
01:20:37,130 --> 01:20:40,010
[Pink Team moves quickly]

2403
01:20:40,100 --> 01:20:43,100
Engfa: They went to the fourth floor
because the elevator shows 4.

2404
01:20:43,100 --> 01:20:44,280
Jeff: They went to the fourth floor.

2405
01:20:44,280 --> 01:20:46,490
[Green Team mobilizes fully]

2406
01:20:44,280 --> 01:20:46,020
Oat: Go, go, go. Let's block them.

2407
01:20:54,490 --> 01:20:58,090
Mike: Let's surround them.

2408
01:20:56,770 --> 01:20:59,450
[They spot Offroad alone]

2409
01:20:59,450 --> 01:21:00,760
Phuak: Chase him.

2410
01:21:00,760 --> 01:21:01,800
Tay: Over here, come on.

2411
01:21:00,890 --> 01:21:03,850
[Phuak and Mike move to block him]

2412
01:21:02,850 --> 01:21:05,700
-Tay: Ink, keep searching, keep going.
-Ink: Then I'll keep looking.

2413
01:21:04,490 --> 01:21:07,130
[Tay and Ink leave the team to find Rabbits]

2414
01:21:05,700 --> 01:21:07,150
-Tay: You keep searching.
-Phuak: We need to lure them over.

2415
01:21:07,150 --> 01:21:10,130
-Phuak: You two go search.
-Mike: Oat is coming up. He's here.

2416
01:21:07,610 --> 01:21:10,010
[Oh no, Oat is on the way!]

2417
01:21:10,840 --> 01:21:13,040
Phuak: We're on higher ground.
Be careful not to fall.

2418
01:21:13,040 --> 01:21:15,090
Mike: Be careful, don't fall, bro. Don't come over.

2419
01:21:13,290 --> 01:21:15,090
[Pink Team holds the high ground to buy time]

2420
01:21:15,090 --> 01:21:19,060
Mike: Don't come over, Oat. Please don't.

2421
01:21:15,970 --> 01:21:18,530
[Oat charges over]

2422
01:21:19,530 --> 01:21:22,690
[You think you can stop me?]

2423
01:21:22,690 --> 01:21:24,480
Mike: Oat, don't do this, Oat.

2424
01:21:22,970 --> 01:21:25,730
[Don't come over…]

2425
01:21:26,490 --> 01:21:30,730
[They're about to clash]

2426
01:21:27,730 --> 01:21:30,390
Oat: Come on, Off, we've got this.
Wait, hold on.

2427
01:21:31,650 --> 01:21:35,170
[Mike tries to face Oat one-on-one]

2428
01:21:36,980 --> 01:21:38,500
Phuak: Off, you…

2429
01:21:37,210 --> 01:21:41,410
[Phuak retreats immediately]

2430
01:21:39,880 --> 01:21:41,500
Oat: That side is a dead end.

2431
01:21:43,410 --> 01:21:46,330
[After retreating, Mike attacks again]

2432
01:21:47,050 --> 01:21:49,890
[When Oat joins in, Mike retreats again]

2433
01:21:52,810 --> 01:21:55,370
[Mike is cornered]

2434
01:21:54,260 --> 01:21:56,170
Mike: I'm surrounded. I'm surrounded.

2435
01:21:56,170 --> 01:21:59,450
[Jeff joins in]

2436
01:22:02,050 --> 01:22:05,450
[He shouts loudly, but it's no use]

2437
01:22:07,650 --> 01:22:10,890
[Mike's name tag is finally ripped]

2438
01:22:14,330 --> 01:22:17,010
[Pink Team shifts the pressure to Engfa]

2439
01:22:17,010 --> 01:22:22,360
-NuNew: Engfa.
-Ink: Tay, rip the name tag. You rip it.

2440
01:22:24,650 --> 01:22:27,530
[The scene falls into total chaos]

2441
01:22:29,290 --> 01:22:31,370
[Ink is surrounded; 2:1]

2442
01:22:31,810 --> 01:22:34,690
[Ink is in danger]

2443
01:22:35,650 --> 01:22:38,010
[She finds an opening and strikes back]

2444
01:22:37,840 --> 01:22:39,360
NuNew: Ink, sorry.

2445
01:22:41,130 --> 01:22:43,130
[Ink's name tag is also ripped]

2446
01:22:43,530 --> 01:22:48,810
PD: Ink and Mike are out.

2447
01:22:43,530 --> 01:22:48,810
[Ink and Mike are out]

2448
01:22:48,810 --> 01:22:52,210
[ Name-Tag Ripping result;
Green Team vs Pink Team]

2449
01:22:52,370 --> 01:22:57,450
[Amid the chaos, Tay runs away quickly]

2450
01:23:03,010 --> 01:23:07,050
[With little time left and 3 teammates already out]

2451
01:23:07,850 --> 01:23:11,570
[Pink Team is in a tough spot]

2452
01:23:12,120 --> 01:23:13,580
Tay: Phuak, where are you?

2453
01:23:16,020 --> 01:23:19,680
Phuak: I'm on the fourth floor in a green room.
The walls are green.

2454
01:23:21,520 --> 01:23:22,450
Tay: Where is it?

2455
01:23:26,960 --> 01:23:28,290
Tay: Is that you, Phuak?

2456
01:23:34,220 --> 01:23:36,740
Phuak: Should we hide separately
or stick together?

2457
01:23:36,740 --> 01:23:38,780
Tay: Let's fight together.

2458
01:23:39,010 --> 01:23:43,050
[What will Pink Team's fate be?]

2459
01:23:39,010 --> 01:23:40,640
Tay: What's our plan?

2460
01:23:43,060 --> 01:23:46,000
Engfa: So, who do they have left now?

2461
01:23:46,000 --> 01:23:47,680
Jeff: They only have 2 people left.

2462
01:23:47,680 --> 01:23:48,820
Engfa: Phuak and…

2463
01:23:48,820 --> 01:23:49,440
Jeff: Tay.

2464
01:23:49,440 --> 01:23:51,490
Jeff: Both of them are strong, to be honest.

2465
01:23:51,490 --> 01:23:54,210
[Right! We can't let our guard down]

2466
01:23:54,620 --> 01:23:57,480
-Oat: How about we go find a Rabbit?
-Offroad: Sure.

2467
01:23:58,370 --> 01:24:03,250
[Green Team isn't in a hurry,
using a stalling strategy instead of chasing]

2468
01:24:04,000 --> 01:24:06,540
-Offroad: Rabbit.
-Oat: Rabbit.

2469
01:24:06,540 --> 01:24:08,820
-Offroad: Found one, found one.
-Oat: Found one.

2470
01:24:08,820 --> 01:24:11,120
-Oat: A Rabbit, there's a Rabbit.
-Offroad: Wild Rabbit.

2471
01:24:11,120 --> 01:24:14,040
-Offroad: How many can play at once? Only one?
-Oat: Let's take the mission for extra time.

2472
01:24:14,040 --> 01:24:14,880
Oat: How many can play at once?

2473
01:24:14,880 --> 01:24:17,880
-Rabbit: One at a time.
-Offroad: Okay, I'll go first.

2474
01:24:18,490 --> 01:24:20,930
[What's the Rabbit mission?]

2475
01:24:21,330 --> 01:24:24,210
[Put your hand into the bottom of the box]

2476
01:24:24,650 --> 01:24:27,770
[Find the batteries]

2477
01:24:28,170 --> 01:24:31,490
[Time limit: 1 minute.
Insert the batteries to start the clock = success]

2478
01:24:31,770 --> 01:24:36,210
[So what's inside the box…]

2479
01:24:37,100 --> 01:24:38,700
Offroad: Okay, I won't look.

2480
01:24:41,730 --> 01:24:46,890
[Already like this before starting?]

2481
01:24:48,010 --> 01:24:54,570
[Offroad is terrified]

2482
01:24:55,060 --> 01:24:57,440
Offroad: Oat, Oat.

2483
01:24:57,440 --> 01:24:58,570
Oat: Did you find it?

2484
01:24:59,460 --> 01:25:01,320
-Oat: Did you get it?
-Offroad: It's squirming.

2485
01:25:01,320 --> 01:25:03,300
-Oat: Is it slippery?
-Offroad: Slippery.

2486
01:25:03,300 --> 01:25:04,720
-Oat: Are you scared?
-Offroad: Pretty scared.

2487
01:25:04,720 --> 01:25:07,540
Oat: Okay, I'm scared too.
Just keep going.

2488
01:25:08,340 --> 01:25:11,400
Offroad: Then why did you ask?
So you're making me do it?

2489
01:25:12,740 --> 01:25:15,200
Offroad: It's fine, it's fine.
Nothing's going to happen.

2490
01:25:15,200 --> 01:25:17,580
Offroad: Ah, what is this? What is this?

2491
01:25:17,580 --> 01:25:20,580
Offroad: Ah, what is this? What is this?

2492
01:25:18,210 --> 01:25:20,570
[Startled]

2493
01:25:20,580 --> 01:25:23,000
Offroad: Ah, what is this? What is this?

2494
01:25:23,170 --> 01:25:24,370
[What's actually inside?]

2495
01:25:24,380 --> 01:25:26,960
Offroad: What is it? No, no.

2496
01:25:24,610 --> 01:25:27,770
[Reveal what's inside the box]

2497
01:25:31,890 --> 01:25:37,050
[They're just… toys]

2498
01:25:37,330 --> 01:25:41,050
[Just toys…]

2499
01:25:42,580 --> 01:25:45,700
Offroad: What is this? What is this?

2500
01:25:47,020 --> 01:25:48,750
Offroad: What is it, what is it?

2501
01:25:50,330 --> 01:25:53,170
[Offroad's mission really strains his voice]

2502
01:25:53,180 --> 01:25:54,640
Offroad: My throat hurts.

2503
01:25:55,560 --> 01:25:57,820
Offroad: I'm scared. What's in here?

2504
01:26:02,220 --> 01:26:03,080
Offroad: What is this?

2505
01:26:03,080 --> 01:26:04,200
Rabbit: You only have 1 minute.

2506
01:26:04,200 --> 01:26:06,130
Offroad: 1 minute? Is it almost up?

2507
01:26:06,420 --> 01:26:08,550
Offroad: Almost up? Is it about to end?

2508
01:26:08,770 --> 01:26:12,010
[Looks like he touched something?]

2509
01:26:18,410 --> 01:26:19,610
Offroad: I found one.

2510
01:26:23,600 --> 01:26:25,060
Offroad: I only found one.

2511
01:26:25,120 --> 01:26:27,080
